    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>1.创建数据库</p><p><code>CREATE DATABASE IF NOT EXISTS school default charset utf8;</code></p><p>1.2删除数据库</p><p><code>drop DATABASE IF EXISTS school;</code></p><p>1.3创建表格</p><p>&lt;<br>create table if not EXISTS t_student(<br>学号 int auto_increment,<br>姓名 varchar(20),<br>性别 bit DEFAULT 1,<br>出生日期 date,<br>PRIMARY key(学号));<br>&lt;<br>1.4删除表格</p><p><code>drop table if EXISTS t_student;</code></p><p>1.5清空表格</p><p><code>TRUNCATE table t_student;</code></p><p>1.6添加表格字段</p><p><code>alter table t_student ADD COLUMN score FLOAT(5, 1) DEFAULT 0;</code></p><p>1.7删除字段</p><p><code>alter table t_student drop COLUMN 出生日期;</code></p><p>2.增删改查</p><p>2.1 增加内容<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-- insert into t_student VALUES( &apos;张三&apos;, , 20);</span><br><span class="line">-- insert into t_student(姓名) values (&apos;小明&apos;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>2.2删除内容<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-- DELETE FROM t_student; -- 删除指定表所有的记录.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-- delete from 表名 where 条件语句; 删除满足条件的数据;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>2.3 修改内容<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-- 改 update 表名 set 字段1=新值1 ,字段2 = 新值2  where 条件语句;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-- update t_student set 姓名 = &apos;小猪&apos; WHERE 姓名 = &apos;小明&apos;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-- update t_student set score = &apos;100&apos; where 姓名 like &apos;小%&apos;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>2.4查找内容</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-- SELECT * from 表名;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-- SELECT * FROM t_student;</span><br><span class="line">-- SELECT 姓名 from t_student;</span><br><span class="line">-- select * from t_student where 姓名 = &apos;小猪&apos;;</span><br><span class="line">-- select * from t_student where score = 20;</span><br><span class="line">-- select 姓名 from t_student where score &gt; 0;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-- 列表重命名</span><br><span class="line">-- select 字段1 as 新字段,字段2 as 新字段2 from 表名;</span><br><span class="line">select 姓名 as &apos;stuname&apos; from t_student;  -- 查询结果重命名</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">select 姓名, if(性别,&apos;男&apos;,&apos;女&apos;) as 性别 from t_student;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-- 列 合并</span><br><span class="line">select concat(姓名,&apos;:&apos;,学号) from t_student;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-- 模糊查询</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">select * from t_student where 姓名 like &apos;%猪%&apos; and score &lt; 101;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-- 排序</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-- select * from 表名 ORDER BY 字段;</span><br><span class="line">select * from t_student ORDER BY score desc;  -- 降序   升 asc</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">select * from t_student ORDER BY 学号 desc , score desc;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-- 限制</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-- select * from t_student LIMIT M offset N; 跳过前4数据,然后取3条</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
